==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# one who [[antagonize]]s, stirs.
# the main source of conflict in a story.
# the archenemy; the hero's [[nemesis]]
# {{biochemistry}} a chemical that binds to a receptor but does not produce a physiological response, blocking the action of [[agonist]] chemicals.

====Antonyms====
* [[protagonist]]
* {{biochemistry}} [[agonist]]

